reviewText: This DVD set has helped me go from 240 to 170 pounds in the past five years.  Each DVD has a 10 minute, a 15 minute and a 30 minute workout.  I gave myself permission to do one 10 minute routine a week to start and i know do 3 30 minute sets a week habitually.  If you want to get your whole body in shape in a gentle slow manner, this is the DVD set for you.
